OL,3,CSnoop Dogg in Wales to watch first
OL,4,CSwansea City game as co-owner
OL,6,FUS rapper Snoop Dogg is in Wales to
OL,7,Fwatch his first Swansea City match
OL,8,Fsince becoming a club co-owner.
OL,10,FThe musician has said he "cannot wait"
OL,11,Fto make his first visit to the club's
OL,12,Fhome ground for their Championship
OL,13,Fmatch against Preston North End on
OL,14,FTuesday, 24 February.
OL,16,FLast July, The Drop It Like It's Hot
OL,17,Frapper joined the likes of US TV host
OL,18,Fand author Martha Stewart and Croatian
OL,19,Ffootballer Luka Modric and became a
OL,20,Fpart-owner of the Championship club.
OL,26,@rD@ZOUrD@fO]
