OL,3,CSnoop Dogg in Wales to watch first
OL,4,CSwansea City game as co-owner
OL,6,FSnoop Dogg, real name Calvin Broadus,
OL,7,Farrived in Swansea on Monday, making a
OL,8,Fvisit to the club's Fairwood training
OL,9,Fground ahead of their match at the
OL,10,FSwansea.com Stadium. He also performed
OL,11,Fa gig in Llansamlet.
OL,13,FSwansea City said the rapper will
OL,14,F"appear pitchside before the game to
OL,15,Flead supporters in a pre-match fan
OL,16,Fdisplay" and visit areas of the local
OL,17,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@HO]
