OL,3,CSnoop Dogg in Wales to watch first
OL,4,CSwansea City game as co-owner
OL,6,FHe has requested a sold-out crowd to
OL,7,Fbe in their seats ahead of kick-off to
OL,8,Ftwirl complimentary towels ` a staple
OL,9,Faction for supporters in American
OL,10,Fsport.
OL,12,FA post on Swansea's official X account
OL,13,Fread: "@SnoopDogg is asking the Jack
OL,14,FArmy to join him in a pre-match towel
OL,15,Ftwirl this evening. Fans are
OL,16,Fencouraged to be in their seats 20
OL,17,Fminutes before kick-off, and to twirl
OL,18,Fthe towels as Snoop walks on the
OL,19,Fpitch."
OL,26,@uD@GOU{D@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
