OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771941809
OL,3,CSnoop Dogg in Wales to watch first
OL,4,CSwansea City game as co-owner
OL,6,FThe post was accompanied by a short
OL,7,Fvideo of the 54-year-old showing how
OL,8,Fhe would like fans to do it.
OL,10,FSnoop Dogg previously told the club's
OL,11,Fwebsite: "I know it has been a long
OL,12,Ftime coming, but I cannot wait to
OL,13,Ffinally make my first visit to Swansea
OL,14,FCity.
OL,16,F"From the moment we talked about me
OL,17,Fbecoming an owner, I have been looking
OL,18,Fforward to the chance to be with you
OL,19,Fall at the Swansea.com Stadium.
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@AOU
