OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1771941809
OL,3,CSnoop Dogg in Wales to watch first
OL,4,CSwansea City game as co-owner
OL,6,F"I have heard so many great things
OL,7,Fabout the atmosphere, especially when
OL,8,Fwe play under the lights.
OL,10,F"When I watched the Wrexham game,
OL,11,Fwhere we showed we are the capital of
OL,12,FWelsh football, the noise in the
OL,13,Fstadium sounded incredible even from
OL,14,Fover 5,000 miles away. I can't wait to
OL,15,Fbe a part of it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@QO]
