OL,3,CSnoop Dogg in Wales to watch first
OL,4,CSwansea City game as co-owner
OL,6,FThe rapper hit headlines earlier this
OL,7,Fmonth at the Winter Olympics, where he
OL,8,Fwas an honorary coach for Team USA as
OL,9,Fwell as a special correspondent for
OL,10,Fbroadcaster NBC, when he asked British
OL,11,Fcurlers Bruce Mouat and Jennifer Dodds
OL,12,Ffor a photo.
OL,14,FSnoop Dogg, known for hits like Gin &
OL,15,FJuice, has had a successful three-
OL,16,Fdecade music career, having topped the
OL,17,FUK charts and received 16 Grammy
OL,18,Fnominations.
